{"tid":2385048,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"捷克政黨領袖反對中企競標核電廠工程　中國大使館氣炸抗議","createTime":"2021-01-28T23:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T23:35:09.000Z","uid":204533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f744c5cdb709a8db9b562cbb2ab69212157e75aa","tid":2385048,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"捷克政黨領袖周三（1/27）達成協議，<strong><span class=\"red\">以國家安全為由不允許中國公司參與該國新核電廠招標，中國駐布拉格使館周四（1/28）對此提出抗議。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n路透報導，捷克政黨領袖周三原則上同意，不應邀請中國競標建造1200 MW核電廠。此決定是聽從安全部門的要求，即捷克可能會遭受來自中選供應商母國的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐布拉格使館在其網站對中國公司可能被排除表示「嚴正關切」，並稱「中方堅決反對捷方將國家安全概念籠統化，這將對中國公司進入捷克公司造成人為阻礙。中方緊急呼籲捷方徹底貫徹市場經濟和公平競爭原則。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，中國廣核集團（China General Nuclear Power Group）與其他4間來自法國、南韓、美國及俄羅斯的公司正在競標這項價值數十億美元，同時也是捷克數十年來最大投資的工程。<br />\n<br />\n儘管北約與歐盟的國安機制同樣反對俄羅斯參與這類工程，但捷克政壇在反對中國競標的同時，至少在現階段仍未將俄國公司排除於外。<br />\n<br />\n捷克政府仍未擬定最終的競標條款。總統齊曼（Milo&scaron; Zeman）一直希望與中國建立良好關係，但隨著在捷克有最大投資的中國華信能源出現問題，令多項工程計劃未能落實。（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"e6ec1a9204f1d2305316e414c20494ca1af9febb","tid":2385048,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210129/S2LC2GKXC5AAPETYLW5OZIBWTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210129%2FS2LC2GKXC5AAPETYLW5OZIBWTI%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w2%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=605398c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210129%2FS2LC2GKXC5AAPETYLW5OZIBWTI%2F&h=60611f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210129/S2LC2GKXC5AAPETYLW5OZIBWTI/</a>"},{"pid":"ac561c5cdd4174fe238f1f9e6e0b0aa1eecf66d1","tid":2385048,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:17:06.000Z","msg":"捷克政府仍未擬定最終的競標條款。總統一直希望與中國建立良好關係。<br />\n<br />\n繼續奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf227360e9a163eb0a79aac19ba3c5168afa0659","tid":2385048,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:19:55.000Z","msg":"中國大使館今日氣炸<br />\n好過中國製核電站起好之後爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bea712e7c617df86ea17b0a528c1ced1e43ee66","tid":2385048,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a7a316355c347297e8d6644b997ebc80fc4f9e","tid":2385048,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac561c5cdd4174fe238f1f9e6e0b0aa1eecf66d1","tid":2385048,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:17:06.000Z","msg":"捷克政府仍未擬定最終的競標條款。總統一直希望與中國建立良好關係。<br />\n<br />\n繼續奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:22:02.000Z","msg":"弱智先會比啲無誠信, 有野心有敵意既獨裁國參與呢啲核電工程<br />\n等於比個春袋人渣住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9106d5ed6aea6c65947312dd42cd09fc4faa448e","tid":2385048,"uid":231725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:22:07.000Z","msg":"中式氣炸"},{"pid":"b6ef3e8f3559e5bed8852cee2cdfd8ff5342e7a3","tid":2385048,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:23:28.000Z","msg":"氣炸師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22820b68994dd67c39b135c8f6156027e5c1a58","tid":2385048,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"請不要干涉別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c53d9eac4b170d2b2407348cf4349be5a02c8fc","tid":2385048,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor